name: Genesis Consumer 000
description: This exact design was initially created for a street art project I started in 1990. By the early 90's, there were thousands of these stickers every where I traveled. My father was an airline pilot and I could fly for free so I took advantage of this as a young person. Over time I have created a narrative around its necessity in the universe. It's current position is an alternative to art and of that which is consumed.
